*note : webflux not working under 2.0.4, java 10 and spring 5.0.8 , as on 10/9/18

so using boot 2.0.3, java 8 and spring 5.0.7 (downloaded from spring.io)

select web reactive dependency

router : allows url and map to handler method
handler : generate response

rest client can be used 
type request : get
link : http://localhost:8080/hello
output : Hello, Spring!


source : spring.io guides
